title: 7 people have commented on how I look like Phreak.  I dunno how to take that.
body: :\  Several friends of mine over the years I've played League have commented on how I look like Phreak.   I dunno if I should take that as a compliment or not!  :P   I haven't read anything in the rules about posting selfies, (will remove thou if mod wants me to) but yeah here is me.   I honestly don't see it but, @Phreak, you have a twin a guess? Oh god the horror?  :P
